snippet.title: The Walking Dead: Our World - Coming Soon to App Store and Google Play
snippet.description:
The first-of-its-kind location based augmented reality mobile game will hit Apple App Store and Google Play soon. Fight walkers on the streets, in the park, on your sofa, wherever and whenever you feel like it.

https://www.facebook.com/thewalkingdeadourworld/
https://www.instagram.com/twdourworld/
https://twitter.com/TWDOurWorld
